@moderator @everyone I've been thinking about getting a new smartwatch, and I'm really interested in finding one that excels in all three areas: battery life, appearance, and water resistance. So far, I haven't found anything that stands out as a clear winner. 

For battery life, I want something that lasts at least a couple of days without needing to charge. Appearance-wise, I love a sleek, modern design that doesn't look too techy. And of course, I need it to be water-resistant so I don't have to worry about it when I'm out and about.

Has anyone here found a smartwatch that checks all these boxes? Or maybe you have some tips on what to look for when shopping for a smartwatch that balances all these factors?
